channel.title: A New Beginning - Searching for a Team
channel.description:
Hello all,
I am looking to start up a server. I am currently searching for a team that will be in itself, successful and willing to work to achieve a goal.
I will be paying for a website, webhosting, and a vps once everything is settled in (Not right off the bat). I have a little knowledge in Java, but not enough to run a successful server on my own.
That is where you come in... I'm looking for a team to help me out and be active.
The base and everything will be discussed within the team itself, once we get a few team members together.
You can contact me through skype at - "Garrett3650" if interested
